title: Lencastre (Dr. Luis Adriano de Magalhães Meneses e)
original_title: Lencastre (Dr. Luis Adriano de Magalhães Meneses e)
body: He was elected a peer of the realm by Madeira for the legislative session from 1890 to 1892.

Madeira: Place where he was elected a peer of the realm

1890-1892: Legislative session as a peer of the realm by Madeira
